  "slug": "distinct-potions",
  "title": "Distinct Potions",
  "description": "Trouble telling your potions apart? Time to give you a helping hand with that.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/distinctpotions/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/distinctpotions/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Discord&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"117\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://x.com/Fusseel\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Twitter&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=x&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"116\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@heyitsfuzs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=YouTube&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"118\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Fuzss\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=GitHub&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"108\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/fuzs_\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=CurseForge&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"143\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Fuzs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Modrinth&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"129\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/distinctpotions/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/about.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Distinct Potions</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> makes potions easier to recognize at a glance. 🧪 With clearer visuals, unique bottle styles, and improved naming, you can finally tell your potions apart without hovering over every single one.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Built for both vanilla and modded content, it helps brewing, storage, and inventory management feel cleaner and more intuitive. ✨</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/distinctpotions/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/features.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🍾 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Unique Potion Bottles:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Greater and extended potions use distinct bottle appearances for easier visual recognition.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🏷️ </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Clear Potion Names:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Potion names directly highlight whether they are greater, extended, or lesser.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🧪 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Distinct Base Potions:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Awkward, mundane, and thick potions gain their own unique colors to stand apart from water bottles.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🎨 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Custom Effect Colors:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Override mob effect colors to restore visuals from older Minecraft versions or create your own style.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⚙️ </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Highly Configurable:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Potion categories are fully customizable and support both vanilla and modded potions through flexible matching rules and tags.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/distinctpotions/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/media.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/distinctpotions/media/1.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/distinctpotions/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/installation.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">INSTALLATION REQUIRED ON CLIENT</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/puzzles-lib\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PUZZLES LIB</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC &amp; NEOFORGE)</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FABRIC API</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC)</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/forge-config-api-port\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FORGE CONFIG API PORT</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC)</span></strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/distinctpotions/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/configuration.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If available for a mod, configuration is possible directly from in-game using the mod menu (requires </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Mod Menu</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> by </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Prospector\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Prospector</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> to be installed on Fabric).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">For manual configuration using an external text editor all files are found at </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">.minecraft/config</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, named as </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-client.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-common.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, or </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-server.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, depending on the type of config. Not all types might exist for a mod, if any at all.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/distinctpotions/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/credits.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌟 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Big thanks to </span><a href=\"https://www.minecraftforum.net/members/AaronBlader12\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">AaronBlader12</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> and their </span><a href=\"https://www.minecraftforum.net/forums/minecraft-java-edition/suggestions/2974948-potion-visual-revamp-make-potions-more-pleasing-to\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Potion Visual Revamp</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> suggestion on the Minecraft Forum, which some parts of this mod are based on.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/distinctpotions/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/pick-up-notifier\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/pickupnotifier/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/easy-anvils\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/bartering-station\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/barteringstation/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/distinctpotions/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/studio.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/distinctpotions/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n",
